# Send ONLY what deploy/Dockerfile COPYs to the build daemon. The repo root also holds
# multi-GB artifacts/data/scratch, the macOS .venv + vendored (macOS) ffmpeg, .git, and a
# local .env secret — none belong in the build context. Whitelisting keeps the context tiny
# and guarantees no .env/media can leak into an image layer.
*

!pyproject.toml
!README.md
!yapper
!yapper_web
!config
!yapper_rpc

# Belt-and-suspenders: never ship caches / compiled junk / secrets even from kept dirs.
**/__pycache__
**/*.pyc
**/*.pyo
**/.env
**/.env.*
